1. Kafka Producer — REAL SYSTEM THINKING
🔥 What a Producer REALLY is

👉 Apache Kafka Producer is:

A reliability component, not just a sender

It guarantees:

Data delivery
Ordering (with key)
Fault tolerance
Backpressure handling
🧠 Internal Flow (IMPORTANT)
App → Serializer → Partitioner → Batch → Broker → Ack
🔍 Breakdown
Step	Meaning
Serializer	Converts object → bytes
Partitioner	Chooses partition
Batch	Groups messages
Broker	Stores data
Ack	Confirms write
🎯 Interview Answer
❓ “Explain Kafka producer flow”

✅ Serialize → partition → batch → send → wait for ack

🟢 2. Producer Configuration — DEEP
🔥 Production Python Config
from kafka import KafkaProducer
import json

producer = KafkaProducer(
    bootstrap_servers='localhost:9092',

    # Reliability
    acks='all',
